The hardware designs, schematic layouts, matrices, and geometric documentation contained within this document—including but not limited to the Zodiac Coil architecture, the Bifilar Conical Caduceus Coil arrays, and the Trailokya Coil configurations—are officially released and protected under the CERN Open Hardware Licence Version 2 – Strongly Reciprocal (CERN-OHL-S v2) (pp. 1, 20, 32).
Any person or entity is welcome to use, study, modify, share, and distribute these designs, or make products based upon them, provided they comply with the strict terms of this strongly reciprocal license.

